window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Liam Montgomery will try everything once. He started his career as a model and turned that opportunity into becoming a bestselling author. The only thing he hasn’t tried is a steady relationship.</p> <p>Not that he’s looking for one.</p> <p>Arden Brady doesn’t get out much.</p> <p>Living with Lupus means sometimes her days aren’t her own. She’s lived her life to the fullest so far, but the one thing she’s never let herself do is fall in love.</p> <p>Then comes Liam.</p> <p>A chance encounter changes the game, and both will have to risk everything they thought important to make this work. Because family secrets and unplanned heartache aren’t the only things trying to tear them apart. But if they’re lucky, the passion between them might just make this romance thing something they can believe in.</p> <p>**Wrapped in Ink is a friends to lovers, who hurt you, opposites attract romance in the Montgomery Ink: Boulder series featuring Liam and Arden. Each book can be listened to as a complete standalone. An HEA is guaranteed!**</p>"; 
